    Still deep in the dark and fearsome innards of the Predacon fortress, 
Paralysis stood watching the mouse. She was preety, quiet, but also dangerous 
at the same time. His attraction to her was starting to cloud his mind.
    Smileing still, "Darkmouse, right? Thats an interesting name. So, tel me 
about yourself." He said, holding his pistol a little more loosely now that 
they were talking. He would take her to Quickstrike soon enough.
